sts.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3662.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The lowdown on Kirak Vil.</span><hr size=1> We didnt bother with any dots or debuffs, I didnt see any kind of regen happening... and he dropped like a rock... I was really kind of embarassed for bringing 2 groups out for this. We only really needed myself (60 pal), 60 warr, 60 rog, and *maybe* a druid/shaman/cleric to heal the warrior once or twice.<br>
<br>
As a comparison, I would say he is no harder (and probably easier) than any random yard trash mob in Umbral Plains. <p><hr width=100%>
